# Blueprint Teknis & Rencana Sprint: LifeGuard Finance (Step 6 - 12)

Dokumen ini menyajikan panduan arsitektur dan spesifikasi kode lengkap untuk mengimplementasikan **Step 6 sampai 12** menggunakan **Clean Architecture** dan **BLoC** (Business Logic Component) di Flutter dengan penyimpanan **Hive (Local-First)**.

---

## Ringkasan Struktur Direktori Clean Architecture
Setiap fitur di bawah akan diatur menggunakan struktur folder berikut:
```text
lib/
├── data/
│   ├── local/
│   │   ├── hive_service.dart
│   │   └── local_keys.dart
│   ├── models/
│   └── repositories/
├── domain/
│   ├── entities/
│   ├── repositories/
│   └── usecases/
├── presentation/
│   ├── bloc/
│   ├── pages/
│   └── widgets/
```

---

## ─── STEP 6: LOCAL STORAGE DENGAN HIVE ───

Hive dipilih sebagai database NoSQL lokal karena memiliki performa sangat tinggi (*high performance key-value store*) dan sangat cocok untuk menyimpan dokumen JSON Map tanpa perlu skema relasional yang rumit pada fase prototipe.

### 1. File: `lib/data/local/local_keys.dart`
```dart
class LocalKeys {
  static const String financeBox = 'finance_box';
  
  // Keys
  static const String userMock = 'user_mock';
  static const String financeProfile = 'finance_profile';
  static const String latestFvsScore = 'latest_fvs_score';
  static const String expenseHistory = 'expense_history';
  static const String simulationHistory = 'simulation_history';
  static const String recommendations = 'recommendations';
  static const String savingsVaults = 'savings_vaults';
  static const String literacyProgress = 'literacy_progress';
  static const String communityPosts = 'community_posts';
  static const String rewardPoints = 'reward_points';
}
```

### 2. File: `lib/data/local/hive_service.dart`
```dart
import 'dart:convert';
import 'package:hive_flutter/hive_flutter.dart';
import 'local_keys.dart';

class HiveService {
  static final HiveService instance = HiveService._internal();
  HiveService._internal();

  late Box _box;

  Future<void> init() async {
    await Hive.initFlutter();
    _box = await Hive.openBox(LocalKeys.financeBox);
  }

  // Menyimpan data bertipe Map/JSON
  Future<void> saveData(String key, dynamic value) async {
    if (value is Map || value is List) {
      // Encode ke JSON string agar aman di Hive untuk tipe data bersarang (nested)
      await _box.put(key, jsonEncode(value));
    } else {
      await _box.put(key, value);
    }
  }

  // Mengambil data
  dynamic getData(String key) {
    final rawData = _box.get(key);
    if (rawData is String) {
      try {
        return jsonDecode(rawData);
      } catch (_) {
        return rawData;
      }
    }
    return rawData;
  }

  // Menghapus data spesifik
  Future<void> deleteData(String key) async {
    await _box.delete(key);
  }

  // Mengosongkan seluruh isi box (Privacy Purge / Reset)
  Future<void> clearAll() async {
    await _box.clear();
  }
}
```

### 3. File: `lib/main.dart` (Inisialisasi Hive)
```dart
import 'package:flutter/material.dart';
import 'data/local/hive_service.dart';
import 'app.dart';

void main() async {
  WidgetsFlutterBinding.ensureInitialized();
  
  // Inisialisasi Layanan Penyimpanan Lokal Hive
  await HiveService.instance.init();
  
  runApp(const LifeGuardApp());
}
```

### 4. Contoh Penggunaan di Repositori (Save & Get Profile)
```dart
import '../../domain/entities/family_finance_profile.dart';
import '../models/family_finance_profile_model.dart';
import '../local/hive_service.dart';
import '../local/local_keys.dart';

class FamilyProfileRepositoryImpl {
  final HiveService _hiveService = HiveService.instance;

  Future<bool> saveProfile(FamilyFinanceProfile profile) async {
    try {
      final model = FamilyFinanceProfileModel.fromEntity(profile);
      await _hiveService.saveData(LocalKeys.financeProfile, model.toJson());
      return true;
    } catch (_) {
      return false;
    }
  }

  Future<FamilyFinanceProfile?> getProfile() async {
    final data = _hiveService.getData(LocalKeys.financeProfile);
    if (data == null) return null;
    return FamilyFinanceProfileModel.fromJson(Map<String, dynamic>.from(data)).toEntity();
  }
}
```

