## ─── STEP 7: FITUR FAMILY FINANCE PROFILE ───

Fitur ini menyediakan input form lengkap bagi pengguna untuk mengumpulkan kondisi fundamental keuangan keluarga secara terperinci.

### 1. Domain Layer (Entity)
```dart
class FamilyFinanceProfile {
  final double fixedIncome;
  final double variableIncome;
  final double routineExpense;
  final double monthlyDebtPayment;
  final double liquidSavings;
  final int dependentsCount;
  final bool hasBpjs;
  final bool hasAdditionalInsurance;

  FamilyFinanceProfile({
    required this.fixedIncome,
    required this.variableIncome,
    required this.routineExpense,
    required this.monthlyDebtPayment,
    required this.liquidSavings,
    required this.dependentsCount,
    required this.hasBpjs,
    required this.hasAdditionalInsurance,
  });

  double get totalIncome => fixedIncome + variableIncome;
}
```

### 2. Data Layer (Model & Repository)
```dart
import '../../domain/entities/family_finance_profile.dart';

class FamilyFinanceProfileModel extends FamilyFinanceProfile {
  FamilyFinanceProfileModel({
    required super.fixedIncome,
    required super.variableIncome,
    required super.routineExpense,
    required super.monthlyDebtPayment,
    required super.liquidSavings,
    required super.dependentsCount,
    required super.hasBpjs,
    required super.hasAdditionalInsurance,
  });

  factory FamilyFinanceProfileModel.fromJson(Map<String, dynamic> json) {
    return FamilyFinanceProfileModel(
      fixedIncome: (json['fixed_income'] as num).toDouble(),
      variableIncome: (json['variable_income'] as num).toDouble(),
      routineExpense: (json['routine_expense'] as num).toDouble(),
      monthlyDebtPayment: (json['monthly_debt'] as num).toDouble(),
      liquidSavings: (json['liquid_savings'] as num).toDouble(),
      dependentsCount: json['dependents_count'] as int,
      hasBpjs: json['has_bpjs'] == 1 || json['has_bpjs'] == true,
      hasAdditionalInsurance: json['has_additional_insurance'] == 1 || json['has_additional_insurance'] == true,
    );
  }

  Map<String, dynamic> toJson() {
    return {
      'fixed_income': fixedIncome,
      'variable_income': variableIncome,
      'routine_expense': routineExpense,
      'monthly_debt': monthlyDebtPayment,
      'liquid_savings': liquidSavings,
      'dependents_count': dependentsCount,
      'has_bpjs': hasBpjs ? 1 : 0,
      'has_additional_insurance': hasAdditionalInsurance ? 1 : 0,
    };
  }

  factory FamilyFinanceProfileModel.fromEntity(FamilyFinanceProfile entity) {
    return FamilyFinanceProfileModel(
      fixedIncome: entity.fixedIncome,
      variableIncome: entity.variableIncome,
      routineExpense: entity.routineExpense,
      monthlyDebtPayment: entity.monthlyDebtPayment,
      liquidSavings: entity.liquidSavings,
      dependentsCount: entity.dependentsCount,
      hasBpjs: entity.hasBpjs,
      hasAdditionalInsurance: entity.hasAdditionalInsurance,
    );
  }

  FamilyFinanceProfile toEntity() => this;
}
```

### 3. Presentation Layer (FamilyProfileBloc)

#### Events
```dart
abstract class FamilyProfileEvent {}
class LoadFamilyProfile extends FamilyProfileEvent {}
class SaveFamilyProfileEvent extends FamilyProfileEvent {
  final FamilyFinanceProfile profile;
  SaveFamilyProfileEvent(this.profile);
}
```

#### States
```dart
abstract class FamilyProfileState {}
class FamilyProfileInitial extends FamilyProfileState {}
class FamilyProfileLoading extends FamilyProfileState {}
class FamilyProfileLoaded extends FamilyProfileState {
  final FamilyFinanceProfile? profile;
  FamilyProfileLoaded(this.profile);
}
class FamilyProfileSaved extends FamilyProfileState {}
class FamilyProfileError extends FamilyProfileState {
  final String message;
  FamilyProfileError(this.message);
}
```

#### Bloc Logic
```dart
import 'package:flutter_bloc/flutter_bloc.dart';
import 'family_profile_event.dart';
import 'family_profile_state.dart';
import '../../domain/repositories/family_profile_repository.dart';

class FamilyProfileBloc extends Bloc<FamilyProfileEvent, FamilyProfileState> {
  final FamilyProfileRepository repository;

  FamilyProfileBloc({required this.repository}) : super(FamilyProfileInitial()) {
    on<LoadFamilyProfile>((event, emit) async {
      emit(FamilyProfileLoading());
      try {
        final profile = await repository.getProfile();
        emit(FamilyProfileLoaded(profile));
      } catch (e) {
        emit(FamilyProfileError('Gagal memuat profil keuangan.'));
      }
    });

    on<SaveFamilyProfileEvent>((event, emit) async {
      emit(FamilyProfileLoading());
      try {
        final success = await repository.saveProfile(event.profile);
        if (success) {
          emit(FamilyProfileSaved());
        } else {
          emit(FamilyProfileError('Gagal menyimpan ke penyimpanan lokal.'));
        }
      } catch (e) {
        emit(FamilyProfileError('Terjadi kesalahan sistem.'));
      }
    });
  }
}
```

### 4. Form Interface (`family_profile_page.dart` dengan validasi)
*   **Validasi**: Angka tidak boleh negatif, pendapatan/pengeluaran pokok wajib diisi dan $>0$.
*   **Navigasi**: Mengarahkan pengguna ke `/dashboard` setelah `FamilyProfileSaved`.

