## ─── STEP 9: EMERGENCY SCENARIO SIMULATION ───

Sandbox krisis menghitung dampak bayangan terhadap tabungan dan proyeksi FVS baru jika terjadi guncangan finansial.

### 1. Model & Enum Simulasi
```dart
enum ScenarioType { phk, medical, cicilan, inflasi, pendidikan, dependent }

class SimulationResult {
  final int beforeFvsScore;
  final int afterFvsScore;
  final int scoreDifference;
  final double survivalMonths;
  final double monthlyDeficit;
  final double remainingSavings;
  final String warningMessage;

  SimulationResult({
    required this.beforeFvsScore,
    required this.afterFvsScore,
    required this.scoreDifference,
    required this.survivalMonths,
    required this.monthlyDeficit,
    required this.remainingSavings,
    required this.warningMessage,
  });
}
```

### 2. SimulationCalculator Service
```dart
import '../../domain/entities/family_finance_profile.dart';
import '../models/simulation_result.dart';
import 'fvs_calculator.dart';

class SimulationCalculator {
  static SimulationResult run({
    required FamilyFinanceProfile profile,
    required ScenarioType type,
    required double parameterValue, // jumlah biaya, persentase inflasi, dll
    required int durationMonths,
  }) {
    final initialFvs = FvsCalculator.calculate(profile).totalScore;
    
    double projectedIncome = profile.totalIncome;
    double projectedExpense = profile.routineExpense;
    double projectedDebt = profile.monthlyDebtPayment;
    double projectedSavings = profile.liquidSavings;
    int dependents = profile.dependentsCount;

    switch (type) {
      case ScenarioType.phk:
        projectedIncome = 0.0; // Kehilangan gaji total
        break;
      case ScenarioType.medical:
        projectedSavings = (projectedSavings - parameterValue).clamp(0.0, double.infinity);
        break;
      case ScenarioType.cicilan:
        projectedDebt += parameterValue; // Cicilan KPR melambung
        break;
      case ScenarioType.pendidikan:
        projectedSavings = (projectedSavings - parameterValue).clamp(0.0, double.infinity);
        break;
      case ScenarioType.dependent:
        projectedExpense += parameterValue; // Kenaikan biaya hidup
        dependents += 1;
        break;
      case ScenarioType.inflasi:
        // Di-handle secara khusus oleh InflationImpactCalculator
        break;
    }

    final shadowProfile = FamilyFinanceProfile(
      fixedIncome: projectedIncome,
      variableIncome: 0,
      routineExpense: projectedExpense,
      monthlyDebtPayment: projectedDebt,
      liquidSavings: projectedSavings,
      dependentsCount: dependents,
      hasBpjs: profile.hasBpjs,
      hasAdditionalInsurance: profile.hasAdditionalInsurance,
    );

    final projectedFvs = FvsCalculator.calculate(shadowProfile).totalScore;
    final deficit = (projectedExpense + projectedDebt) - projectedIncome;
    final double survival = deficit > 0 ? (projectedSavings / deficit) : 99.0;

    return SimulationResult(
      beforeFvsScore: initialFvs,
      afterFvsScore: projectedFvs,
      scoreDifference: initialFvs - projectedFvs,
      survivalMonths: double.parse(survival.toStringAsFixed(1)),
      monthlyDeficit: deficit > 0 ? deficit : 0.0,
      remainingSavings: projectedSavings,
      warningMessage: survival < 3.0 ? 'Peringatan: Dana darurat Anda diproyeksikan habis kurang dari 3 bulan!' : 'Kondisi dana darurat aman.',
    );
  }
}
```

---

## ─── STEP 10: INFLATION IMPACT CALCULATOR ───

Modul ini diintegrasikan ke dalam sandbox krisis untuk menyimulasikan kenaikan harga bahan pokok sebesar persentase tertentu.

### 1. Logic & Integrasi
```dart
class InflationImpactCalculator {
  static SimulationResult calculate({
    required FamilyFinanceProfile profile,
    required double inflationRate, // e.g. 0.15 untuk 15%
    required int durationMonths,
  }) {
    // Biaya esensial pokok melonjak
    final increasedExpense = profile.routineExpense * (1 + inflationRate);
    final shadowProfile = FamilyFinanceProfile(
      fixedIncome: profile.fixedIncome,
      variableIncome: profile.variableIncome,
      routineExpense: increasedExpense,
      monthlyDebtPayment: profile.monthlyDebtPayment,
      liquidSavings: profile.liquidSavings,
      dependentsCount: profile.dependentsCount,
      hasBpjs: profile.hasBpjs,
      hasAdditionalInsurance: profile.hasAdditionalInsurance,
    );

    final initialFvs = FvsCalculator.calculate(profile).totalScore;
    final projectedFvs = FvsCalculator.calculate(shadowProfile).totalScore;
    
    final totalOutflow = increasedExpense + profile.monthlyDebtPayment;
    final deficit = totalOutflow - profile.totalIncome;
    final double survival = deficit > 0 ? (profile.liquidSavings / deficit) : 99.0;

    return SimulationResult(
      beforeFvsScore: initialFvs,
      afterFvsScore: projectedFvs,
      scoreDifference: initialFvs - projectedFvs,
      survivalMonths: double.parse(survival.toStringAsFixed(1)),
      monthlyDeficit: deficit > 0 ? deficit : 0.0,
      remainingSavings: profile.liquidSavings,
      warningMessage: survival < 3.0 
          ? 'Warning! Akibat kenaikan inflasi, daya tahan dana darurat Anda kritis di bawah 3 bulan.' 
          : 'Daya tahan dana darurat cukup memadai.',
    );
  }
}
```

